Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:04.73,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.42,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,It's a statement from the group responsible for the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:11.47,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,They're demanding public recognition of contractors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.99,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,as well as greater authority and rights as contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.24,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Is this really what they said?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:23.91,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,I don't know. However, there's no denying that acts of terrorism have been committed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:27.63,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,and that a group called the Evening Primrose exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.37,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Evening Primrose...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:39.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Is BK201 related to them in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:46.20,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Kirihara, what I'm about to tell you is strictly confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:47.44,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:56.74,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The leader of this terrorist group is a former MI6 conspirator known as February, Messier Code UB001.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:01.27,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Five years ago, she was in the front lines at Heaven's Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:08.22,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It didn't look like he went out to see an ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.74,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Did he look like a man who wanted revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:17.84,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Officials were concerned that he still had feelings for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:19.96,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,but it seems they were worried about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.18,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,I guess we should observe him a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.94,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What happened between those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:31.72,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,It's best you don't know for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.32,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped. I'll give you a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:41.28,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,Hei was betrayed by that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.73,DTB-Default,Agent,0,0,0,,and the rest of his team died in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:51.79,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The first star ever recorded at that time was hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.72,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,A myriad of stars began to shine as if they were reacting to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.72,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Included in that group was BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:09.10,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Immediately following that incident, a 1,500 kilometer radius of South America disappeared from the face of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.11,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.89,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:23.85,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,There's no hope for any of you if you start drinking during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:26.02,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.92,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,,Drinking while the sun's out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:31.45,DTB-Default,Joshua,0,0,0,,is what the gusto of life is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.26,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.06,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,My, off to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:37.94,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.87,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,It's good to know that you have your priorities in order, Li-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.70,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.42,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Hey, handsome! Why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.66,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry... I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.55,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Why not? Live a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:52.72,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't drag an honest young man like him into your worthless lifestyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.69,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Come on, now! On your feet! Go! Meeting adjourned! Move! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.69,DTB-Overlap,Man A,0,0,0,,Party crasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.34,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Sir, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:14.44,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,You can't leave until the bill has been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:17.40,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,I told you that I forgot my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.58,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,I'll bring it tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.89,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:21.91,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,That does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.99,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.56,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.39,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm Sakurai of the Nakazawa family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.94,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Nakazawa family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:44.81,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Pay your bill and get the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:48.69,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You're asking for trouble if you start pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.65,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Let your fists do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.41,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.02,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.14,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Hey, you... Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.25,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.73,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.86,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.22,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,You fucking punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:25.14,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um... Please calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.87,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.62,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,M-My store...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.53,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.13,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.25,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.02,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Do you really want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.02,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.81,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're making quite a scene, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.57,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,One must pay his dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.95,DTB-Default,Punk,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:12.96,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.70,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.73,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.51,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Um... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.28,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Sakurai Kenji-san of the Nakazawa family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.18,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'm Li Shun Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.56,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.50,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You're Chinese, as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.60,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,"As I thought?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:40.23,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Wasn't that Chinese martial arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.96,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You were dodging the enemy as easily as a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:46.99,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I bet you could have taken care of him even if Aniki didn't come, Li-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You'd shout "acho!" while doing it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.82,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:54.02,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Come on, you don't have to be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.15,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.38,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.13,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:10.86,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kenji, a gangster who's been underestimated isn't much of a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.96,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.94,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Thanks for looking out for him, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.52,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Well, it's part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.42,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Take this and treat him to a decent meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.13,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:26.81,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.38,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.67,DTB-Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.25,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.96,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:55.46,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You sure do eat a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.52,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Could this be the secret behind your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.60,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Like I said, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.80,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Stop being such a tease and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.64,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Are you really sure you were okay with beef bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:16.08,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Since I have some money on me, I can take you to gentlemen's clubs if you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.72,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No, I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.67,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I see. Distancing yourself from women is the secret behind your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.29,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.84,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll make sure we reach your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.68,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:36.83,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I caused a lot of trouble for you today, so I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.82,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.29,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.64,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.46,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.86,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You don't have much, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:09.04,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Well, all I do is sleep when I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.40,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san, what do you do with your spare time whenever you're not working?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.46,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.56,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Didn't you come to Japan to train?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.46,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No, I came to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.28,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Oh, you're a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.84,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.90,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Oh, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:35.01,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,The usual? That noise just shook the entire room, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.96,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,It's pretty early, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.77,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's probably the same people from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:44.09,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Can you even focus on studying with this noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.46,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.98,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You're practically at their mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.89,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Let me resolve this issue permanently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.78,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.39,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "what is it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:12.34,DTB-Default,Joshua,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.76,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Sakurai of the Nakazawa family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.06,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,,Nakazawa family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:26.70,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! What the hell were you thinking, playing a guitar that loudly in a shoddy room with paper-thin walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.25,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.72,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,What the hell were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:35.86,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.37,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Yeah, that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.37,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.53,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,I bet you're all hungry from causing this ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.12,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.90,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You're from the Philippines?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.15,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Are you working in Japan by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:14.93,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Yeah. My parents and siblings are still over there, so I send them money every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.53,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,It must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:22.36,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Not really. The Japanese are all rich perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.63,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.89,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Why are you in Japan, rock star?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:33.65,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,,I'm a missionary who came here to preach about the essence of rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.66,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Wow! Essence, huh? That's pretty far out, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.09,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.52,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.55,DTB-Default,Joshua,0,0,0,,I came from Israel to study Japanese animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.20,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You came all the way here just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.95,DTB-Default,Joshua,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Japanese anime is the best in the world. Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:51.67,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Your explanations are always too long, so let me stop you right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.81,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,This is a pretty diverse apartment, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:11:01.38,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm fluent in seven different languages because of these tenants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Wow, this place sure is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.53,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Maybe I should live here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.90,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Right, Li-sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.86,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:13.44,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You just ate tons of beef bowls...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.87,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Do you want seconds, Li-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.75,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Ah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.49,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Isn't he done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.62,DTB-Default,All,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.69,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,,Now that we're full...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:30.42,DTB-Default,Joshua,0,0,0,,Let's start the second round!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.54,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Are you guys in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:37.32,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Booze? Great! Right, Li-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:41.24,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I have an appointment to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.31,DTB-Default,Man A,0,0,0,,That guy is really unsocial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.97,DTB-Default,Louis,0,0,0,,We barely talked to him until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.04,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:59.76,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Some people don't like to interact with others. Come on, let's drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.34,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.90,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Don't you think there's a lonely aura emanating from Li-san's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.73,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Seventeen A Love Song Sung from a Trash Heap... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:19.94,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Hitotsubashi, it's not that I dislike a man like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.79,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:26.75,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,However, I will not tolerate internal feuds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.43,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.99,DTB-Default,Ohshita,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:30.99,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Ohshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.96,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,I know you've been taking Ohshita's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:45.69,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Rest assured. I have no intention of inciting this conflict any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:51.05,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Stay out of sight for a while. I'll eventually assign you to a proper position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:55.51,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,I know about your potential more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.06,DTB-Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.66,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'll make sure it's engraved within my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.07,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hitotsubashi, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.57,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Did he show up at the club already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:07.77,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.69,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.66,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The goods should be brought there within the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.45,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Be careful not to interfere with the transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:21.75,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,We know it'll all be in vain if we screw up the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:24.57,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,That aside, who is that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.07,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.06,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.78,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.39,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I don't want any distractions during the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.68,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.28,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.86,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.11,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,They fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:58.59,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Good! Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.19,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:03.29,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You provided me with shelter from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:07.47,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I could have called for a cab with that hundred grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.59,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I didn't think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.72,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san, you're a strange person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:18.26,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Let's meet up for a meal sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.12,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.82,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.39,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Li-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.99,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,I had trouble reaching you since you don't have a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:41.16,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late notice, but we won't be able to work for three nights, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.26,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:48.01,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Construction work. Remember the problems we were having with the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.13,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:54.27,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,You'll be on paid leave while the construction's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.20,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.73,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,A-Aniki, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.36,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I said I'm going to divide the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.57,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,The organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:13.22,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm indebted to the boss, but he's become senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:17.65,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,A gangster in need of stability isn't much of a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.58,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.96,DTB-Default,Hitotsubashi,0,0,0,,I have a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:32.22,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kenji, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.06,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,A-Aniki, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.16,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.09,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.67,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.15,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.29,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.70,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,A-Aniki, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.00,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,A doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.72,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Doll? She's human!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.85,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:29.70,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's a state-of-the-art doll that will do anything it's told to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.11,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,There are rich people out there who want these kinds of toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:40.21,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Take care of her for the next two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.76,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,If you don't feed her, she'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.35,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You'll have to take care of her excretions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.64,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,She's precious merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.56,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Make sure you keep her clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.96,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Merchandise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.03,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:05.56,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Don't get caught up with dirty thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.19,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:18.49,DTB-Default,Underling,0,0,0,,Why did you get him involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:23.88,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,The merchandise might become tainted unless an idiot like him takes care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:29.97,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He doesn't have the balls to betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:40.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I thought I'd have to kill someone since he said he had a job for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.97,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:56.39,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.45,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You don't understand Japanese, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.81,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.36,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What are they going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:27.37,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,BK201-related information? I already told you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:31.20,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm sure you have, but it still doesn't make sense for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:36.32,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The mysterious group that calls itself E.P.R., their statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.44,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,and BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:44.79,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Are they enemies or are they working independently?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:47.91,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What's his objective in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.16,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,We don't know anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,yet they're telling us to go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:56.50,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Say, did Hoshimi-sama say anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.86,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Any new analytical data...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.45,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.36,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,I was pulling all-nighters until a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.97,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about work while I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:08.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.03,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Misaki, aren't you off-duty tomorrow, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:12.35,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:16.38,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,You're probably not doing anything, so why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.79,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:36.67,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Are you sure you weren't noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.85,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,We're not that careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.09,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Why's the doll missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.34,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Who knows? It was probably stolen from them, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.02,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Stolen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.20,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.13,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:53.42,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's been internal conflict within the Nakazawa family recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.98,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Yin, can you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:19:59.71,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:00.88,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.64,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Let's back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:05.95,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,It's best not to look into it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:11.52,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Whether we continue the mission or not isn't a decision we can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.90,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'm going to submit a request, so everything's on hold until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.50,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.60,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Can we use your place as a hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The jewel in hand gives off a clear, uncolored glow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:49.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,its purity calling near the specter of devastation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Their two worlds were never supposed to have crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:59.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They have nowhere to go, and their flight will continue without end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:03.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't even want to know what lies ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:08.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the boy lies down in the trash heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,540)}Episode Eighteen A Love Song Sung from a Trash Heap... (Part Two)